<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>A Love Undone by Time</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
            background-color: #faf8f5; /* Warm, soft cream paper color */
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.8;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #111111;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .intro-box {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0dacb;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .intro-box p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            color: #888888;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333333;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .letter-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .letter-item {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .letter-date {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #888888;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        .letter-link {
            color: #111111;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 2px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .letter-link:hover {
            color: #666666;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 100px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #999999;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0dacb;
            padding-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>A Love Undone by Time</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">Letters to my baby girl</div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- Your introductory text for visitors -->
        <section class="intro-box">
            <p><strong>Welcome to this quiet corner of the internet.</strong></p>
            <p>This is an ongoing collection of emails and letters written to my daughter, using her nickname to protect her privacy as she grows. It is a mother's heart preserved in words, meant to outlast me so she will always know how deeply she is loved.</p>
            <p>I have left this space completely open to the public. If you have found your way here because you are longing for your own mother, or for a mother's warmth, please know that these words are for you, too. You are welcome to rest here a while.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Where your future letters will be linked -->
        <section>
            <div class="section-title">The Archive</div>
            <ul class="letter-list">
                <li class="letter-item">
                    <span class="letter-date">June 2026</span>
                    <a class="letter-link" href="#">Letter One: Coming Soon</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>Eternally out there. Made with love for my little one.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
